OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775578269
OL,3,CWales Captain Aaron Ramsey announces
OL,4,Cretirement from football
OL,6,FAaron Ramsey has announced he is
OL,7,Fretiring from football after a career
OL,8,Fspanning nearly two decades.
OL,10,FIn a statement, the midfielder and
OL,11,FWales Captain said it was not an easy
OL,12,Fdecision to make, while thanking his
OL,13,Fcolleagues and the fans.
OL,15,FThe statement read: "This has not been
OL,16,Fan easy decision to make. After a lot
OL,17,Fof consideration, I have decided to
OL,18,Fretire from football.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
