OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775578269
OL,3,CWales Captain Aaron Ramsey announces
OL,4,Cretirement from football
OL,6,F"Firstly, I want to start with Wales.
OL,7,FIt has been my privilege to wear the
OL,8,FWelsh shirt and experience so many
OL,9,Fincredible moments in it.
OL,11,F"It would not have been possible
OL,12,Fwithout the incredible input of all
OL,13,Fthe managers I have played under and
OL,14,Fall the staff who have helped me in
OL,15,Fmany ways.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
