PN,46103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775578269
OL,3,CWales Captain Aaron Ramsey announces
OL,4,Cretirement from football
OL,6,F"To the Red Wall. You have been there
OL,7,Fthrough thick and thin! You have been
OL,8,Fthere through the highs and lows, and
OL,9,Fyou have been an essential and
OL,10,Findispensable part of our success. I
OL,11,Fcan't thank you enough. We've been
OL,12,Fthrough everything together and it's
OL,13,Fbeen an honour to represent you.
OL,14,FDiolch.
OL,16,F"Secondly, thank you to all the clubs
OL,17,FI've been lucky enough to play for.
OL,18,FThank you to all the managers and
OL,19,Fstaff that have helped me be able to
OL,20,Flive my dream and play at the highest
OL,21,Flevel.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
