CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775578269
OL,3,CWales Captain Aaron Ramsey announces
OL,4,Cretirement from football
OL,6,F"And a huge thank you to my wife and
OL,7,Fchildren and all my family. Without
OL,8,Fyou by my side throughout, none of
OL,9,Fthis would have been possible."
OL,11,FRamsey was first signed with Cardiff
OL,12,FCity in 2007 at the age of 16 and then
OL,13,Fwent on to make his first appearance
OL,14,Ffor Wales' senior team at the age of
OL,15,F17 a year later. He moved to Arsenal
OL,16,Fthat same year.
OL,18,FThe 35-year-old left Cardiff City in
OL,19,F2025 following their relegation to
OL,20,FLeague One and represented Pumas in
OL,21,Fthe Mexican league for several months.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
