OL,3,CWales Captain Aaron Ramsey announces
OL,4,Cretirement from football
OL,6,FHe made a return to the national side
OL,7,Ftowards the end of last year after
OL,8,Finjury ruled him out for more than 12
OL,9,Fmonths.
